accessibility.text: You need ONE number that represents all prices of goods and services you  will need to buy
To decide which salary is better, you need to know how much you can buy with that salary
With more information about prices in each country you can make an even better choice
Some things are more expensive, others are cheaper…
This price alone, helps  you make a better decision
